<p>I also ran into the situation where I had to remove an element from <code>Array</code>. <code>.indexOf</code> was not working in Internet&nbsp;Explorer, so I am sharing my working <code>jQuery.inArray()</code> solution:</p>

<pre><code>var index = jQuery.inArray(val, arr);
if (index &gt; -1) {
    arr.splice(index, 1);
    //console.log(arr);
}
</code></pre>
